WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.180
And then you connect with your breath and you also stabilize your

2
00:00:05.180 --> 00:00:05.480
eyes.

3
00:00:07.160 --> 00:00:08.800
You stabilize the eye.

4
00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:16.480
The eye is an expansion of the brain.

5
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:23.160
The eye is an expansion of the third ventricle.

6
00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:28.000
And there you are...

7
00:00:28.065 --> 00:00:28.745
