14
00:01:26.195 --> 00:01:31.215
You could, you think of someone who comes to mind

15
00:01:31.215 --> 00:01:36.335
like that, to whom you want to send love or kindness, simply.

16
00:01:38.015 --> 00:01:44.615
You think of someone to whom you could, through a

17
00:01:44.615 --> 00:01:50.555
thought like that, imagine that you can send them well-being,

18
00:01:50.555 --> 00:01:52.075
